ssionals and salon distributors under the revlon professional brand mens shampoos conditioners gels and other hair care and grooming products for use and sale by professional salons under the american crew brand unisex hair products under the dfi brand and nail enhancement systems as well as nail color and treatment products and services for use by professional nail salon industry under the cnd brand in addition it provides multicultural haircare products under the crème of nature brand and professional hair products under the orofluido uniqone and intercosmo brands the company markets its products to retailers chain drug and food stores chemist shops hypermarkets general merchandise stores department stores and specialty cosmetic stores as well as to the us government military exchanges and commissaries the company was founded in  and is headquartered in new york new york revlon consumer products corporation is a subsidiary of revlon inc detailed description one new york plazanew york ny united statesfounded in  employees phone  wwwrevloncom key executives for revlon consumer products corp mr christopher h peterson chief operating officer age  mr gianni pieraccioni executive vice president and global president of revlon consumer division age  mr sennen pamich executive vice president and global president of revlon professional division ms mitra hormozi chief compliance officer executive vice president and general counsel mr michael t sheehan senior vice president deputy general counsel and secretary compensation as of fiscal year  revlon consumer products corp key developments lorenzo delpani announces not to stand for reelection as board member of revlon inc and revlon consumer products corp apr   revlon inc and revlon consumer products corporation filed with the sec on march   the company and lorenzo delpani entered into a transition and separation agreement and release on march   in connection with the transition of his duties and responsibilities as the companys former president and chief executive officer on april   the company and mr delpani entered into an amendment to the tsa in connection with the tsa amendment the parties have agreed that mr delpani will not stand for reelection to serve as a member of companys board at revlons  annual stockholders meeting scheduled to be held on june   and will also cease to serve as a member of revlon consumer products corps board as of that date revlon consumer products corporation announces executive changes apr   on april   the board of directors of revlon inc revlon and together with its subsidiaries including without limitation revlon consumer products corporation rcpc the company elected juan r figuereo as executive vice president and chief financial officer of revlon and rcpc effective as of april   mr figuereo succeeds mr roberto simon in such position whose resignation from the company was effective on february   mr figuereo  most recently served as executive vice president and chief financial officer of nii holdings inc from october  through october  revlon consumer products corp announces executive changes mar   revlon consumer products corporation elected fabian t garcia as the companys president and chief executive officer effective april   mr garcia was also appointed to serve as a member of revlon incs and rcpcs boards of directors effective april   mr garcia replaces lorenzo delpani who served as the companys president and chief executive officer from november  through march   prior to joining the company mr garcia served in senior executive positions at the colgatepalmolive company including most recently as its chief operating officer global innovation and growth europesouth pacific  hills pet nutrition a position he held since  with expanded responsibility for hills pet nutrition beginning in  similar private companies by industry company name region  laboratories inc united states  luxury goods inc united states bc llc united states  nutrition llc united states